The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Big match on Aug.18 

A STAFF REPORTER 

Calcutta: The CFL Premier Division Derby match between East Bengal and Mohun Bagan will be held on August 18, a day ahead of the scheduled August 19. The match will start at 5 pm at the Salt Lake Stadium under the lights. 

Meanwhile, responding to the clubs call for neutral referee for the match, Englishman Dave Robers the IFA secretary Subrata Dutta informed. 

Roy, Basu injured 

Bata SCs Shankar Roy and Gopal Basu of Milan Bithee suffered serious injuries during their CFL group B match in Shyamnagar on Monday. 

They were involved in an aerial collision, and fell unconscious. Both were taken to SSKM Hospital and were reported to be stable and released late at night. Milan Bithee won 4-0. 




